fields.description: # Curriculum In this project we'll learn how to fly a Super Star Destroyer. We'll have both theoretical and practical lessons on a Super Star Destroyer Mark XCVIII. This is **by far** the *greatest* lesson _**evah**_! #### First lesson going all out. #### Second lesson 1. Assembling the SSD101 crew 2. Getting a spare engine (not issued by default with every SSD, but trust me, you want this). #### Third lesson Killing rebel scum. Code injection
fields.title: Super Star Destroyer 101
